==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[sext-]]'' '''six''', + ''[[-illion]]'', from [[million]]; ''i.e.,'' the sixth [[power]] of a million, 10<sup>36</sup>

===Pronunciation===
*{{Rhymes|ɪljən}}

